text: Paula Linda Liniņa (born 6 May 2001) is a Latvian footballer who plays as a midfielder for Sieviešu Futbola Līga club FS Metta and the Latvia women's national team. ==References== Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Latvian women's footballers Category:Latvia women's international footballers
